OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776777070
OL,3,CUK must act on allergies after
OL,4,C'decades of neglect', charities and
OL,5,Cdoctors say
OL,7,FThe government must improve allergy
OL,8,Fprevention, diagnosis, and management,
OL,9,Faccording to a group of charities,
OL,10,Fdoctors, and patients, who say the UK
OL,11,Fhas some of the highest allergy rates
OL,12,Fin the world.
OL,14,FThe group, which has found that
OL,15,Fallergies affect 39% of children and
OL,16,F30% of adults in the UK, has developed
OL,17,Fa National Allergy Strategy, which was
OL,18,Fpresented to Westminster this week.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776777070
OL,3,CUK must act on allergies after
OL,4,C'decades of neglect', charities and
OL,5,Cdoctors say
OL,7,FThe strategy, which is the first UK-
OL,8,Fwide framework for improving allergy
OL,9,Fcare, aims to tackle "decades of
OL,10,Fpolicy neglect", according to the
OL,11,FNational Allergy Strategy Group (NASG).
OL,13,FIt aims to improve awareness and
OL,14,Fgovernance of allergies, such as
OL,15,Fasthma, hay fever, food and drug
OL,16,Fallergies, and calls for all four UK
OL,17,Fgovernments and the NHS to recognise
OL,18,Fallergic disease as a major long-term
OL,19,Fcondition.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776777070
OL,3,CUK must act on allergies after
OL,4,C'decades of neglect', charities and
OL,5,Cdoctors say
OL,7,F"For too long, despite the scale of
OL,8,Fthe problem, too little has been done
OL,9,Fto develop solutions," said NASG chair
OL,10,FProfessor Adam Fox.
OL,12,F"This strategy focuses on system-level
OL,13,Fchange, embedding allergy into
OL,14,Fnational policy, strengthening safety
OL,15,Fin everyday environments and improving
OL,16,Faccountability across health,
OL,17,Feducation, food and workplace
OL,18,Fsettings".
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@VO]tD@AOUzD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776777070
OL,3,CUK must act on allergies after
OL,4,C'decades of neglect', charities and
OL,5,Cdoctors say
OL,7,FThe group, led by Charity Allergy UK,
OL,8,Fthe British Society for Allergy and
OL,9,FClinical Immunology, Anaphylaxis UK
OL,10,Fand the Natasha Allergy Research
OL,11,FFoundation, worked with 150 experts to
OL,12,Fdevelop the strategy.
OL,14,FIt says allergy care and treatment are
OL,15,F"dramatically under-resourced," with
OL,16,Fmost GPs receiving no training in
OL,17,Fallergy.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776777070
OL,3,CUK must act on allergies after
OL,4,C'decades of neglect', charities and
OL,5,Cdoctors say
OL,7,F"There is a postcode lottery of care,
OL,8,Finsufficient numbers of allergy
OL,9,Fdoctors, long waiting times for
OL,10,Fallergy testing and service gaps,"
OL,11,Fsaid Tanya Ednan-Laperouse, founder
OL,12,Fand trustee of the Natasha Allergy
OL,13,FResearch Foundation.
OL,15,FEdnan-Laperouse's daughter Natasha
OL,16,Fdied after eating a Pret baguette
OL,17,Fcontaining sesame in 2016.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
