CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776777070
OL,3,CUK must act on allergies after
OL,4,C'decades of neglect', charities and
OL,5,Cdoctors say
OL,7,FAllergy considerations should be
OL,8,Fembedded into health, education, food
OL,9,Fregulation, environment, employment
OL,10,Fand transport policy frameworks,
OL,11,Faccording to the strategy.
OL,13,FAction on respiratory allergies, for
OL,14,Fexample, should be built into cross-
OL,15,Fsector policies to improve air quality.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
