CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776777070
OL,3,CUK must act on allergies after
OL,4,C'decades of neglect', charities and
OL,5,Cdoctors say
OL,7,FThe strategy also outlines steps to
OL,8,Fimprove testing for and medical
OL,9,Frecords of drug allergies and
OL,10,Fpromoting safe allergen management,
OL,11,Fespecially for food allergies, which
OL,12,Fare a common cause of a life-
OL,13,Fthreatening reaction called
OL,14,Fanaphylaxis.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
