PN,30208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776777070
OL,3,CUK must act on allergies after
OL,4,C'decades of neglect', charities and
OL,5,Cdoctors say
OL,7,FEdnan-Laperouse said the UK should
OL,8,Fhave an allergy "tsar" to deliver the
OL,9,Fplans outlined in the strategy.
OL,11,FThe NASG is also campaigning for a
OL,12,F#2.7 million clinical trial to find
OL,13,Fnew and better treatments for people
OL,14,Fwith food allergies on the NHS, she
OL,15,Fadded.
OL,17,FA Department of Health and Social Care
OL,18,Fspokesperson said they are committed
OL,19,Fto improving allergy care and are
OL,20,Fworking with members of the NASG and
OL,21,Fconsidering its recommendations.
OL,26,@pD@QOUpD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
