PN,30209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776777070
OL,3,CUK must act on allergies after
OL,4,C'decades of neglect', charities and
OL,5,Cdoctors say
OL,7,FNew guidance set to come into force in
OL,8,FSeptember 2026 will require schools to
OL,9,Fstock spare adrenaline auto-injectors
OL,10,Ffor use in emergencies, provide
OL,11,Fallergy awareness training for all
OL,12,Fstaff and have a policy for supporting
OL,13,Fchildren with medical conditions that
OL,14,Fincludes having healthcare plans for
OL,15,Findividuals.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776777070
OL,3,CUK must act on allergies after
OL,4,C'decades of neglect', charities and
OL,5,Cdoctors say
OL,7,FThe new rules have been dubbed
OL,8,F"Benedict's Law" in memory of five-
OL,9,Fyear-old Benedict Blythe, from
OL,10,FStamford in Lincolnshire, who died
OL,11,Ffrom an anaphylactic reaction at
OL,12,Fschool in December 2021.
OL,14,FThe NASG is also campaigning to
OL,15,Fimplement a second law, Owen's Law,
OL,16,Fnamed after a Sussex teenager who died
OL,17,Ffollowing an allergic reaction to food
OL,18,Fhe ate at a burger bar. The law would
OL,19,Frequire written allergen information
OL,20,Fat the point of ordering across food
OL,21,Foutlets.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
